Type: Package
Package: magickx
Title: Extension of the R-Package magick
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Hauke",
           family = "Sonnenberg",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "hauke.sonnenberg@gmx.de",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9134-2871"))
Description: Image manipulation based on the magick package.  It contains
    functions to select or remove horizontal or vertical stripes from an
    image. These may be used to cut off undesired areas from an image,
    e.g. as preparation for optical character recognition (OCR).
